<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr" class="add-preferences">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Home</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Bree+Serif" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="opacity-wrapper">
    <div class="profile-heading">
      <h1>Market Profile</h1>
      <form class="home-icon-wrapper" action="/homepage" method="get">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" role="button" type="submit"><i class="fas fa-2x fa-home"></i></button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-address">
      <h2>Evanston Farmers Market</h2>
      <hr />
      <div class="profile-inline">
        <div class="profile-inline-div">
          <p>1800 Maple Avenue, Evanston, IL 60201</p>
          <p>(847)-448-8045</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-inline-div">
          <form class="profile-button" action="/order" method="get">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Order</button>
          </form>
          <div class="profile-button">
            <a href="mailto:someone@example.com?Subject=Hello" target="_top" role="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary" name="profile-contact">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-information">
      <h2>Featured Farmers</h2>
      <hr />
      <div class="profile-info-wrapper">

        <div class="profile-info-div">
          <img class="profile-image" src="images/profile/Image1.jpg" alt='Image of Market' align="right">
          <p><b>Salman Johnson </b> &#8212;
            Coming from St. Louis, Salmam Johnson's has been growing fruits and vegetables his whole life.
            He comes from a long line of farmers and is said to have soil flowing through his veins.
            Caring for and providing the best produce to his loyal customers, and he hopes to make you one of them.
          </p>
          <p><b>Joe Dugon</b> &#8212;
            Born and raised in Kansas, Joe Dugon is Salmans best friend. He has dedicated his life
            to raising and caring for livestock. With 30 years of knowledge under his belt, Dugon always
            carries the highest quality produce. He always claims that the secret to his success stems from
            the personal relationships he has with each of his animals, and lots of coffee.
          </p>
          <h2>Reviews</h2>
          <span id="filled-star">&#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;</span>
          <p><b>Anonymous </b> &#8212;
            The farmers here really care about what they're selling, amazing people and amazing produce!
          </p>
          <span id="filled-star">&#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;</span> <span id="empty-star">&#9734;</span>
          <p><b>Souradip </b> &#8212;
            I am a big fan of Salman's livestock. He always has the best stuff in town and he's always been a good friend.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-featured-foods">
      <h2>Featured Foods</h2>
      <hr />
      <div class="profile-row">
        <div class="preference">
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="images/preferences/apple.png" alt="apple">
          </div>
          <div class="icon-caption">
            apple
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preference">
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="images/preferences/grapes.png" alt="grapes">
          </div>
          <div class="icon-caption">
            grapes
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preference">
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="images/preferences/beef.png" alt="beef">
          </div>
          <div class="icon-caption">
            beef
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preference">
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="images/preferences/cheese.png" alt="cheese">
          </div>
          <div class="icon-caption">
            cheese
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preference">
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="images/preferences/ice-cream.png" alt="ice-cream">
          </div>
          <div class="icon-caption">
            ice-cream
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="location-map">
      <iframe class="map" frameborder="0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=KEY=Evanston+Farmers+Market,Evanston+IL" allowfullscreen>
      <!-- Api key removed -->
      </iframe>
      <hr>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("partials/footer"); -%>
